
==Korean==
===Particle===
'''을''' (eul)

# grammatical marker for the direct [[object]] of a verb, follows words which end in a consonant. 

Note: Use [[를]] instead, for words which end in a vowel.

====Synonyms====
*[[를]] (reul, follows vowels)

====Translations====
*Hebrew: [[את]]
*Japanese: [[を]] (o)
*Spanish: [[a]] (only used when the object is a person)